= Locations =

This page documents all locations in Final Fantasy IV (SNES version) for the Super Nintendo.

== Overview ==

Final Fantasy IV spans three worlds: the Overworld (surface), the Underworld (land of dwarves), and the Moon. The game features extensive dungeons and a world-spanning journey.

